NOTE ON BUNDLED THIRD-PARTY ARTIFACTS
=====================================

The ``raw_source/`` directory bundles original material produced by
Prof. Ray C. Fair (Yale / Cowles Foundation) and distributed from
<https://fairmodel.econ.yale.edu/>. Those files — ``FP.FOR``, ``FP.EXE``,
``fminput.txt``, ``fmdata.txt``, ``MC.INP``, ``SHR.INP``, ``SHRDDD.DAT``,
the ``.DAT`` data files, and the PDF documents under ``07_docs/`` — are
NOT covered by the MIT license above. They are included unmodified under
the terms of the upstream distribution: Fair's site permits download and
use for academic purposes but retains copyright.

Anyone redistributing those files must follow Fair's original terms. The
Python code under ``src/pyfair/`` and ``tests/`` is a clean-room port and
is covered by the MIT license.
